exclusion_criteria:
Presence of neoplastic (primary or metastatic) lung lesions, manifested as nodules, masses, consolidations, septal thickening (lymphatic carcinomatosis) or pleural thickening;
Chest CT with the presence of movement, acquisition or reconstruction artefacts that make it impossible to apply the segmentation algorithms;
CT exams with low quality pulmonary segmentation, or slice thickness greater than 3.0 mm.

inclusion_criteria:
Articles related to SO or communities where developers search for support; OR 
Articles related to the association or recommendation or suggestion or link of software project artifacts; OR 
Articles that address the use of software development information to find SO posts;
